text: Jeju Province officially Jeju Special Self-Governing Province (Jeju-teukbyeol- jachi-do) is divided into 2 administrative cities (haengjeong-si) and further into 7 towns (eup), 5 townships (myeon), and 31 administrative neighborhoods (haengjeong-dong).
